  m_Name: MilitaryRecord_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 37
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i #5 \u2014 K\xEDp c\xF4ng binh"
  category: 5
  content: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD k\xEDp c\xF4ng binh. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i g\u1EAFn 8 charges
    \u1EDF tr\u1EE5 c\u1EA7u. Nh\u01B0ng khi chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB r\xFAt, m\u1ED9t
    th\xE0nh vi\xEAn b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn. Anh ta bi\u1EBFn ngay trong xe. Xe \u0111\xE2m
    v\xE0o r\xE0o, 2 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EBFt. T\xF4i l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng
    s\xF3t duy nh\u1EA5t. Charges \u0111\xE3 g\u1EAFn nh\u01B0ng t\xF4i ch\u01B0a
    k\xEDch n\u1ED5 \u2014 t\xF4i c\u1EA7n l\u1EC7nh. Nh\u01B0ng radio kh\xF4ng li\xEAn
    l\u1EA1c \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. T\xF4i \u0111ang \u1EA9n trong t\xF2a nh\xE0 b\xEAn
    c\u1EA7u. N\u1EBFu ai \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c: bom \u0111\xE3 g\u1EAFn
    nh\u01B0ng ch\u01B0a k\xEDch. C\u1EA7n b\u1ED9 k\xEDch n\u1ED5. T\xECm trong
    t\xF2a cao t\u1EA7ng g\u1EA7n \u0111\xF3."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
